text: Guru Brahmanand (24 December 1908 - 16 May 1973) is an Indian guru and spiritual master from Chuhar Majra village of Kaithal district, Haryana. He was born in Hindu Ror family to father Badama Ram and mother Rami Devi. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1973 deaths Category:Indian Hindu saints
title: Guru Brahmanand
